    "body": "You can do JSON-RPC over IPC. Do not mistake JSON-RPC for being HTTP only, previously we implemented JSON-RPC over TCP/IP but due to much complaints we switched to HTTP. IPC will allow sending and receiving over the same channel. Kind of like WebSockets but without the overhead of TCP/IP :-)\n\nIPC issue https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/pull/1165\n",
